data.text:
There are few things to rival the majesty and grandeur of the Nordic landscapes, from its climbing peaks to its dense forests aged with secrets. Yet, there is a playfulness and joy that comes from wandering its hills and dales. No wonder it is an Instagram paradise! Enjoy the northern skoger og fjell (forests and mountains) beneath a starry sky and remind yourself of the joy of Nordic wanderlust with this fun, nature-inspired shirt.

***Please note that due to the current COVID-19 pandemic, the Premium style is currently unavailable. Subscribe to stay up-to-date on all updates as well as promotions, upcoming products, and more!***

Style

Each shirt comes in either a Standard and Premium option. Keep in mind that some color options may be limited to one style or the other.

Our Standard shirts are made of a super soft cotton with a tear-away label, providing you a true-to-size retail fit. However, don’t let the name Standard fool you. Even the mighty Eitri and Brokkr would be proud to have forged such a shirt as this.

Our Premium shirts are so comfy that even the gods themselves will be jealous! Made of ultra-soft TriBlend material, this extra-lightweight shirt provides a retail fit that will leave you never wanting to take it off!

Shipping

All our shirts are made to order, so please allow 7-12 days for shipping. All orders come with tracking so you can follow along with the progress of your shirt and receive updates for a more accurate delivery window.

Grab your axe, pack your lefse, and join us in our goal to share all things Nordic with the world!

From the medieval to the modern, our passion for sharing and teaching is at the heart of all we do. We want to not only bring excellent Norse products to thicken your beard and please the gods, but to help you learn a little more about these countries, their cultures, histories, and languages.

So stig på and welcome to The Norse Among Us!
